016]]\n**Runners-up (4): [[2002 J.League Cup|2002]], [[2004 J.League Cup|2004]], [[2011 J.League Cup|2011]], [[2013 J.League Cup|2013]]\n*'''[[Japanese Super Cup]]'''\n**'''Winners: (1):''' [[2006 Japanese Super Cup|2006]]\n**Runners-up (4): [[2007 Japanese Super Cup|2007]], [[2015 Japanese Super Cup|2015]], [[2017 Japanese Super Cup|2017]], [[2019 Japanese Super Cup|2019]]\n\n===Continental===\n*'''[[AFC Champions League]]'''\n**'''Winners (2):''' [[2007 AFC Champions League|2007]], [[2017 AFC Champions League|2017]]\n**Runners-up (1): [[2019 AFC Champions League|2019]]\n\n===International===\n*'''[[FIFA Club World Cup]]'''\n**Third place (1): [[FIFA Club World Cup 2007|2007]]'''\n*'''[[Suruga Bank Championship]]'''\n**'''Winners (1):''' [[2017 Suruga Bank Championship|2017]]\n\n===Individual Awards===\nSee ''[[Individual Award Winners (Urawa Red Diamonds)]]''\n\n==Players==\n\n===Current squad===\n''As of 18 February 2020.''<ref>https://www.urawa-reds.co.jp/english/team.html</ref>\n{{football squad start}}\n{{football squad player|no= 1|nat=JPN|pos=GK|name=[[Shusaku Nishikawa]]}}\n{{football squad player|no= 2|nat=BRA|pos=DF|name=[[Maur\u00edcio Ant\u00f4nio]]}}\n{{football squad player|no= 3|nat=JPN|pos=MF|name=[[Tomoya Ugajin]]}}\n{{football squad player|no= 4|nat=JPN|pos=DF|name=[[Daisuke Suzuki (footballer)|Daisuke Suzuki]]}}\n{{football squad player|no= 5|nat=JPN|pos=DF|name=[[Tomoaki Makino]]|other=[[Captain (association football)|Vice-captain]]}}\n{{football squad player|no= 6|nat=JPN|pos=DF|name=[[Ryosuke Yamanaka]]}}\n{{football squad player|no= 7|nat=JPN|pos=MF|name=[[Kazuki Nagasawa]]}}\n{{football squad player|no= 8|nat=BRA|pos=MF|name=[[Ewerton (footballer, born 1992)|Ewerton]]|other=on loan from [[FC Porto|Porto]]}}\n{{football squad player|no= 9|nat=JPN|pos=FW|name=[[Yuki Muto]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=10|nat=JPN|pos=MF|name=[[Y\u014dsuke Kashiwagi]]|other=[[Captain (association football)|Captain]]}}\n{{football squad player|no=11|nat=CUW|pos=