o]]\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Shinji Ono]]\n*{{flagicon|FR Yugoslavia}} [[\u017deljko Petrovi\u0107]]\n\n'''[[2006 FIFA World Cup|World Cup 2006]]'''\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Alessandro Santos|Alex]]\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Shinji Ono]]\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Keisuke Tsuboi]]\n\n'''[[2010 FIFA World Cup|World Cup 2010]]'''\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Yuki Abe]]\n\n'''[[2014 FIFA World Cup|World Cup 2014]]'''\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Shusaku Nishikawa]]\n\n'''[[2018 FIFA World Cup|World Cup 2018]]'''\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Wataru Endo]]\n*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Tomoaki Makino]]\n*{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Andrew Nabbout]]\n\n==Former players==\n{{See also|Category:Urawa Red Diamonds players|Category:J.League players}}\n\n===International capped players===\n{|\n|- style=\"vertical-align: top;\"\n|\n::'''[[Japan Football Association|JFA]].'''\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Masayuki Okano]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Shinji Ono]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Keisuke Tsuboi]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Alessandro Santos|Alex]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Masahiro Fukuda]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Yuichiro Nagai]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Nobuhisa Yamada]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Marcus Tulio Tanaka]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Tatsuya Tanaka (footballer)|Tatsuya Tanaka]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Teruaki Kurobe]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Tomoyuki Sakai]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Hiromitsu Isogai]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Ry\u014dta Tsuzuki]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Naohiro Takahara]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Hajime Hosogai]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Yuki Abe]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Makoto Hasebe]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Keita Suzuki]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Tadanari Lee]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Ryota Moriwaki]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Naoki Yamada]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Genki Haraguchi]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Shusaku Nishikawa]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Wataru Endo]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Tomoaki Makino]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Shinzo Koroki]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Y\u014dsuke Kashiwagi]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Tomoya Ugajin]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} [[Yuki Muto]]\n:*{{flagicon|JPN}} 